cmd-removewalleddecals-desc = Removes decals hidden beneath walls on a grid.
cmd-removewalleddecals-help =
    Usage: {$command} [gridId]
    Removes decals beneath walls on the specified grid, or on your current grid if no grid is provided.
cmd-removewalleddecals-no-grid = Grid with id {$grid} does not have GridComponent.
cmd-removewalleddecals-missing-grid-entity = Provided grid does not exist!
cmd-removewalleddecals-removed = Removed {$count} decals.
